            <cato:entity-ref entity-type="act" value="Social Security Act/s:1115A">Section 1115A of the Social Security Act</cato:entity-ref> (<cato:entity-ref entity-type="uscode" value="usc/42/1315a">42 U.S.C.
		1315a</cato:entity-ref>)</cato:entity> is repealed.</text>
      </subsection>
